1732
01:21:08,493 --> 01:21:10,078
<font size="" color="">
¿Sobre qué?

1733
01:21:10,161 --> 01:21:11,788
<font size="" color="">
Matarlos.

1734
01:21:11,871 --> 01:21:13,498
<font size="" color="">
