1740
01:21:24,217 --> 01:21:25,343
<font size="" color="">
Lo sé.

1741
01:21:25,427 --> 01:21:27,595
<font size="" color="">
Es hermoso.

1742
01:21:27,679 --> 01:21:29,472
<font size="" color="">
Vamos a purificar este país

1743
01:21:29,556 --> 01:21:32,809
<font size="" color="">
