sobre los explosivos?

1852
01:27:03,348 --> 01:27:04,349
<font size="" color="">
No.

1853
01:27:04,474 --> 01:27:05,934
<font size="" color="">
A la mierda.

1854
01:27:06,059 --> 01:27:07,143
<font size="" color="">
